      @Deprecated public static List<org.apache.uima.cas.FeatureStructure> create(org.apache.uima.cas.CAS cas, org.apache.uima.cas.Type type)
      Deprecated.
      Use cas.select(type).asList()
      Create a Collection of the given type of feature structures. This collection is backed by the CAS, either via an CAS.getAnnotationIndex(Type) or FSIndexRepository.getAllIndexedFS(Type).
      Parameters:
      cas - the CAS to select from.
      type - the type of feature structures to select. All sub-types are returned as well.
      Returns:
      a Collection of the given type of feature structures backed live by the CAS.
      See Also:
      • Order of selected feature structures
